    <briefdescription>
<para>Class representing accessibility relations. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Class connecting one source object with multiple target objects with usage of specific relation type.</para>
<para>A remote target object (i.e. one belonging to a different process) can be represented in terms of a <ref refid="classDali_1_1Accessibility_1_1ProxyAccessible" kindref="compound">ProxyAccessible</ref>.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Accessibility_1_1Accessible_1a5053aa95b5e34f8f83e2e4c7d0cd9c79" kindref="member">Dali::Accessibility::Accessible::Accessible</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>Dali::Accessibility::Accessible::RelationType </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
